Package fi.tuni.olvander.citybicyclejourneys

Class CityBicycleJourneys

java.lang.Object
fi.tuni.olvander.citybicyclejourneys.CityBicycleJourneys
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.springframework.boot.CommandLineRunner
@SpringBootApplication public class CityBicycleJourneys extends Object implements org.springframework.boot.CommandLineRunner
The main class for the City Bicycle Journeys App.

For importing City Bicycle Stations and Bicycle Journeys into the H2
database as well as for showing commands for opening the app in the
browser and commands for REST requests.

Implements the CommandLineRunner interface.

1.21

    • getBicycleJourneyData

      public Optional<BicycleJourney> getBicycleJourneyData(ResultSet rs) throws Exception
      For getting Bicycle Journey data from the Bicycle Journey CSV files
      for saving to the database. Excludes the Bicycle Journeys having a
      distance or a duration less than 10 meters or seconds dynamically.
      Parameters:
      rs - A ResultSet from the Csv().read() method
      Returns:
      An Optional Bicycle Journey object
      Throws:
      Exception - Throw this if the ResultSet data cannot be parsed
